 1mhz clock speed of the nes cpu measured in machine cycles as well? Which cpu is more powerful, and which one is clocked higher? And is saying the gameboy clock speed is 4.4.1943mhz, the same thing as saying the new clock speed is 21.5mhz? What would the master systems cpu clock be in machine cycles?</div>

